   <category name='objects'>

      <section name='horse'>

         <para number='1' comment='Pet horse - player'>
         You reach up and gently stroke the horse's nose.  It snorts softly in response and nuzzles your hand gently, clearly enjoying your touch.
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='Pet horse - roomex'>
         %s reaches up and softly strokes the horse's nose.
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='Feed horse - player'>
         You reach into your pocket and pull out an apple, offering it up to the horse.  It leans down and slowly begins munching, its lips delicately tickling your palm until it has eaten up the entire apple.
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='Feed horse - roomex'>
         %s offers up an apple to the horse, which slowly munches away until it is entirely gone.
         </para>

         <para number='5' comment='Groom horse - player'>
         You notice a stiff-bristled brush nearby, pick it up, and begin to brush the horse down, starting at the neck and slowly working your way to his rear, then switching sides and repeating.  The horse stands calmly and allows you to brush him down, occasionally neighing softly.
         </para>

         <para number='6' comment='Groom horse - roomex'>
         %s reaches down, picks up a brush lying in the sand and begins brushing down the horse from neck to rear, focusing first on one side, then the other.
         </para>

         <para number='7' comment='Ride horse - player'>
         The horse leans down and allows you to climb up, bareback.  Once you are settled it rises up, whinnies and suddenly takes off like a shot down the beach.  You cling to its heaving neck as it tears down the beach.  Its hooves thunder through the surf, kicking up salt water and wet sand as the sea air whips through your hair.
         </para>

         <para number='8'>
         After an exhilarating sprint down the beach, the horse turns and slowly trots back, allowing you to dismount where you started.
         </para>

         <para number='9' comment='Ride horse - roomex'>
         %s gingerly climbs upon the back of the horse, which whinnies loudly and suddenly takes off down the beach, taking the rider for a wild ride through the surf.
         </para>

         <para number='10'>
         The horse then returns and allows %s to dismount.
         </para>

         <para number='11' comment='examine horse'>
         A lofty, elegantly-formed Appaloosa mare, with a roan coat, spotted hindquarters and odd dark vertical stripes on its hooves.  It is without saddle or other marking except for a single sash around its neck, emblazoned with the name "Angel."
         </para>

      </section>

